<! [CDATA[
Alrosa Logo
Alrosa is a Russian group of diamond mining companies that specialize in exploration, mining, manufacture, and sale of diamonds. The company leads the world in diamond mining by volume. Mining takes place in Western Yakutia, the Arkhangelsk region, and Africa. Alrosa is Russia’s leading diamond mining and distribution company, accounting for 95% of Russian diamond production and 27% of global diamond extraction. The company’s headquarters are located in Mirny and Moscow.
